    "en": {
      "title": "A STF player who connects with people",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A Special Task Force (STF) soldier also joined the people during the popular uprising in Colombo today (09).",
        "He removed his uniform on the protest field and joined the people with loud applause.",
        "Meanwhile, during the protest in Maharakama this morning, one of the traffic policemen took off his helmet and threw it on the street, chanting \"Arakalayatta Jayave Wa\" (Victory to the Struggle) and joined hands with the protestors."
      ],
